              <title xml:lang="en" ref="http://syriaca.org/work/72">The Gospel of <persName>S.
                                        Matthew</persName>, according to the Peshitta
                                version</title>
              <note>It begins with ch. ix. 7.</note>
              <note>The Ammonian sections and Eusebian canons are marked with red
                    ink in the text of this volume, and there is a
                    harmony at the foot of each page.</note>              
