                                <condition>
                                    <list>
                                        <item>
                                            <p>Vellum, about 12 3/8 in. by 10, of which foll. 1 and 9 are much
                                                mutilated. Leaves are wanting at the beginning. Each page is divided into two columns,
                                                containing from 28 to 32 lines. These leaves belong to 
                                                <bibl>Add. 14,451*<ptr target="http://syriaca.org/manuscript/123"/></bibl>,
                                                but have been long bound up with this manuscript.
                                                </p>
                                        </item>
                                    </list>
